en-us: Let us know how we did at [$SUPPORT_EMAIL](mailto:$SUPPORT_EMAIL)
How can I help you?

The COVID-19 Vaccine Eligibility bot aggregate data from trusted and verified sources to help understand your vaccine eligibility. This system does not provide medical advice and is not intended for use as a diagnostic or treatment tool for any disease, including COVID-19. You can provide feedback by emailing [$SUPPORT_EMAIL](mailto:$SUPPORT_EMAIL)
